version_description:
This version optimizes multiple product user experiences, making it even easier to use.
1. Add frequently used stickers，quickly find the stickers you want;
2. Support the search department, quickly locate the department structure, find people more convenient;
3. View more than 100MB Excel charts, design drawings, etc. without downloading, you can zoom in or view horizontally;
4. Quickly view PSD, AI and other design files on macOS without installing software, look at the picture faster!

User experience optimization
1. Long press on the selected picture in the chat to quickly mark the picture;
2. The search results support a secure watermark to prevent the screenshot from leaking out;
3. Add more interesting Emoji expressions, and chats could be fun.

Office collaboration optimization
1. The report function supports monthly statistics and reminders, so the monthly work is clear at a glance;
2. Ding Drive upgrade supports file search in any directory, so finding file is more convenient!

User experience optimization

1. The layout of the organizational structure in the address book is redesigned, and the departmental structure is clearer;
2. When members are invited to join the company/team, members can upload photos (badge, selfie, etc.) to prove their identity. It is easier for administrators to judge the authenticity of joining membership;
3. When login DingTalk the first time, you can use the mobile phone verification code to log in;
4. The voice message in the chat supports the progress bar drag and play, no longer have to worry about waiting for 60 seconds to listen from the beginning;

Approval function optimization

1. The approval management permission is subdivided into templates, and the administrator can only edit and export the templates that have permissions to them;
2. When the approver resigned, the approval process is not interrupted, and the main administrator can forward the unfinished approval form on the report export page.

